Is it canceled 'cause of the rain?

638
00:38:37,767 --> 00:38:39,765
When was it actually supposed to start?

639
00:38:39,825 --> 00:38:40,823
And I got all dressed up.

640
00:38:40,847 --> 00:38:42,646
There's no way it's happening.

641
00:38:43,011 --> 00:38:44,759
It's too crowded here anyway.

642
00:38:45,806 --> 00:38:48,430
I read online that your sunshine girl is amazing.

643
00:38:48,475 --> 00:38:49,784
100% success rate.

644
00:38:49,808 --> 00:38:50,939
Uh, yeah.

645
00:38:51,375 --> 00:38:55,704
