681
00:42:13,478 --> 00:42:16,004
This abnormal cold snap is affecting agriculture.

682
00:42:18,128 --> 00:42:20,098
Oh, that submission?

683
00:42:20,265 --> 00:42:21,709
Yes, we received it.

684
00:42:21,744 --> 00:42:24,468
Look, I'm sorry, but we decided to pass.

685
00:42:24,523 --> 00:42:27,685
I see. Thank you, and, uh...

686
00:42:28,121 --> 00:42:30,879
we have other pieces in the
works for, you know, next time.

687
00:42:38,752 --> 00:42:39,467
Hmm.

688
00:42:41,096 --> 00:42:42,461
Yeah, what?

689
00:42:55,945 --> 00:42:57,879
Hello. Mamiya residence.

690
00:42:57,995 --> 00:42:59,521
Hi. It's Keisuke.

691
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:03,945
I'm sorry to bother you, but it's regarding my visit.

692
00:43:05,073 --> 00:43:06,414
You're late again, Kei.

693
00:43:06,439 --> 00:43:07,933
And this is an important interview.

694
00:43:09,464 --> 00:43:10,340
Bad mood?

695
00:43:10,610 --> 00:43:12,176
Did you get rejected? Meow.

696
00:43:12,248 --> 00:43:13,261
Where's the kid?

697
00:43:15,164 --> 00:43:17,460
What do you mean, busy with his other job?

698
00:43:17,516 --> 00:43:19,144
No wonder he's been slacking.

699
00:43:19,454 --> 00:43:20,768
Just leave him alone.

700
00:43:20,932 --> 00:43:22,203
It's not like we're busy.

701
00:43:22,368 --> 00:43:24,378
He took in a stray cat without asking.

702
00:43:24,521 --> 00:43:25,594
Like you took him in?

703
00:43:25,919 --> 00:43:26,577
Huh?

704
00:43:27,009 --> 00:43:28,383
I know why you did it.

705
00:43:28,408 --> 00:43:29,783
He reminds you of yourself.

706
00:43:31,562 --> 00:43:34,835
Plus, how much could it be costing
you to pay the kid each month?

707
00:43:35,782 --> 00:43:37,146
What, 30,000 yen?

708
00:43:37,171 --> 00:43:38,132
Cheapo.

709
00:43:38,244 --> 00:43:40,149
Actually, 3,000.

710
00:43:40,371 --> 00:43:43,914
Uh... what?! Are you serious?! That's slave labor!

711
00:43:43,939 --> 00:43:45,471
Is that even legal?

712
00:43:45,496 --> 00:43:48,816
You're gonna get sued by the Department
of Labor. Young people love suing.

713
00:43:48,840 --> 00:43:51,139
You know what? Actually, I-I
think I'm gonna report you myself.

714
00:43:51,282 --> 00:43:52,927
One, he gets to live with us for free.

715
00:43:53,036 --> 00:43:55,635
Two, we pay for his food and his phone bill.

716
00:43:56,230 --> 00:43:57,121
It's a sweet deal.

717
00:43:57,146 --> 00:43:58,456
Oh, God.

718
00:44:00,204 --> 00:44:02,182
Well, no wonder he got another job.

719
